        <date>2025-08-27</date>
        <security>
            <item><![CDATA[<p>No known security issues.</p>]]></item>
        </security>
        <fix>
            <item>No bugfixes in this version.</item>
        </fix>
        <language>
            <item>Deutsch</item>
            <item>English</item>
        </language>
        <addition>
            <item>Introduced <code>HandlerUtilsTrait</code> to centralize common routing utilities.</item>
        </addition>
        <change>
            <item>Removed DI-based registration of routing handlers; handlers are now managed locally in the Router.</item>
            <item>Provider reduced to core-style service registration only (MVC, Dispatcher, Router, Component).</item>
        </change>
        <remove>
            <item>Removed duplicate <code>isSefEnabled()</code> and <code>trim()</code> implementations from handlers.</item>
        </remove>
        <note>
            <item>Refactoring of routing architecture to improve maintainability and stability.</item>
        </note>
